Class EcolawToUpdTemplate

java.lang.Object

EcolawVisitor
public final class EcolawToUpdTemplate
extends Object
implements EcolawVisitor

This class represents an EcolawVisitor, capable of translating an eco-law (whose variables has been bound) into a set of SPARQL Update statements.
